> Using Eligibility

# Tests: Eligibility derived tests inferred from 523B policy example in extracted-tests.yaml — 2026-03-27

## Test: drv_001 — A1E 2025: client adjusted $1,707.50 below standard; DOL adjusted $1,879 just outside 10% band (upper=1878.25) — manual verification required

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDrv001:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestDrv001:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $3,500
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
    -- household_type: A1E
    -- benefit_year: 2025
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $11,529
    -- gross_earned_income: $3,843
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = ManualVerification)
  assertion (result.reasons = [])
```

## Test: drv_002 — A1E 2025: client adjusted income exactly $1,795 = income limit; DOL same — approve (≤ limit passes)

```catala
#[test]
declaration scope TestDrv002:
  result scope Eligibility.EligibilityDecision

scope TestDrv002:
  definition result.client_data equals Eligibility.ClientData {
    -- gross_earned_income: $3,675
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
    -- household_type: A1E
    -- benefit_year: 2025
  }
  definition result.d_o_l_record equals Eligibility.DOLRecord {
    -- dol_earned_income_available: true
    -- dol_quarterly_earnings: $11,025
    -- gross_earned_income: $3,675
    -- federal_exclusions: $0
    -- eitc_exclusion: $0
    -- irregular_earned_income: $0
    -- student_earned_income: $0
    -- student_monthly_limit: $0
    -- non_needs_based_unearned_remainder: $20
    -- impairment_work_expenses: $0
    -- blind_work_expenses: $0
    -- self_support_exclusion: $0
  }
  assertion (result.eligible = Approve)
  assertion (result.reasons = [])
```

